import numpy as np

make random dataset and visualization¶

In [2]:
from sklearn.datasets import make_classification
X, y = make_classification()
X, y = pd.DataFrame(X), pd.DataFrame(y, columns=['target'])
data = pd.concat([X, y], axis=1)
sns.pairplot(data, vars=data.columns[:-1], hue='target', palette='cubehelix')

Sklearn preprocessing module¶

Normalization¶

  • Normalization은 data를 0과 1 사이의 값으로 바꿔 표준편차로 바꿔준다.
In [7]:
from sklearn.preprocessing import Normalizer
nm = Normalizer()
nm.fit(data.x.values.reshape(1, -1), data[data.columns[-1]])
Out[7]:
Normalizer(copy=True, norm='l2')

Standard Scale¶

  • StandardScaler는 각 특성의 평균을 0, 분산을 1로 변경하여 모든 특성이 같은 크기를 갖도록 한다.
In [13]:
X, y = make_blobs()
X, y = pd.DataFrame(X, columns=['x', 'y']), pd.DataFrame(y, columns=['target'])
data = pd.concat([X, y], axis=1)
In [14]:
from sklearn.preprocessing import StandardScaler
ss = StandardScaler()
ss_ft = ss.fit_transform(data.iloc[:, :-1].values)
ss_data = pd.concat([pd.DataFrame(ss_ft), y], axis=1)
sns.pairplot(ss_data,
             vars=ss_data.columns[:-1],
             hue='target',
             palette='winter')
Out[14]:
<seaborn.axisgrid.PairGrid at 0x7f32a9482e80>

모델 평가¶

cross validation¶

In [15]:
from sklearn.neighbors import KNeighborsClassifier
from sklearn.model_selection import cross_val_score
In [16]:
X, y = make_blobs(random_state=4)
X, y = pd.DataFrame(X, columns=['x', 'y']), pd.DataFrame(y, columns=['target'])
data = pd.concat([X, y], axis=1)
knn = KNeighborsClassifier()
score = cross_val_score(knn, data.iloc[:, :-1], data[data.columns[-1]], cv=10)
score, np.mean(score)
